The paper deals with the development of a deep learning algorithm for liver segmentation in CT scans. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) categories. The use of convolutional neural networks (CNNs) and graph cut also suggests the involvement of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) techniques. The paper also mentions the use of volume measurement, which could potentially fall under multimedia (cs.MM) or medical imaging (cs.MS) categories.
